name: UAE Radio
short_description:
Developed in UAE for UAE !

UAE Radio is a simple and handy application that allows you to stream the 
most popular radio stations across U.A.E. Now, you can use this 
lightweight, efficient and quick application in order to stream the most 
popular radio stations across the United Arab Emirates
without switching through websites to hear your favourite stations !

The following stations are available for streaming :

Dubai 92
Radio 1
Dubai Eye
Channel 4 FM
Coast 103.2
Radio 2
Virgin Radio
Abu Dhabi Classic FM
Star FM
FM Emarat
Radio Abu Dhabi
Rock Radio UAE
AL Arabiaya
AL Khaleejiya
Radio 4 89.1 FM
JOSH FM
Radio Shoma
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Please uninstall / remove previous versions before installing another version.
